{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CloverPit</strong> is a rogue-lite horror game, where playing at the Slot Machine is your only chance to survive.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/Title_Image.png?t=1736261666\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up in a rusty, narrow cell, standing over a dangerously unstable grate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Someone has kidnapped you, demanding payment, and your only way out is to play the Slot Machine and pay off your debt.<br>Don\u2019t let yourself fall \u2014literally\u2014 into ruin!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/The_Slot_Machine_x2.gif?t=1736261666\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manipulate the Slot Machine and earn more coins than you should! Turn the odds in your favor with various lucky charms found along the way. Bend the rules, break the game, and pay your captor to ultimately earn your freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong></strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/The_Real_Deal_x2.gif?t=1736261666\" /><strong><br>MAIN FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Horror escape-room atmosphere</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roguelite structure with 100 + items and synergies that impact each run</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meta-progression with multiple endings and unlockable power-ups</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intriguing risk-reward scenarios</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rewarding dopamine rushes</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A mysterious plot and atmosphere</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>AND NOW:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/Survive_x2.gif?t=1736261666\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>IS THIS GAMBLING?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cloverpit includes a representation of a &quot;Slot Machine&quot;, but it\u2019s not a Slot Machine Simulator. This rogue-lite game revolves around a fictional &quot;Slot Machine&quot; rigged in your favor, and it's all about buying the right powerups to break the game. <br>Unlike a real casino, the villain in this game might as well be an angel!\u00a0Your captor will never ask for real money! <br>We do not condone gambling, and if you struggle with it, please consider seeking support\u2014there\u2019s no shame in asking for help!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736261666","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/page.bg.jpg?t=1736261666","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/a356e6c996513ab9932c1808dab5b841c1be26f5/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736261666","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/a356e6c996513ab9932c1808dab5b841c1be26f5/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736261666","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CloverPit</strong> is a rogue-lite horror game, where playing at the Slot Machine is your only chance to survive.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/Title_Image.png?t=